content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1221.9 - Throwing or dropping objects from windows or down stairwells, shafts, etc. prohibited

State Regulations

The occupant shall not drop or throw anything from or out
of any window in the terminal and shall not drop or throw anything into any
ventilating or elevator shaftway, stairwell or other opening in the
terminal. Notes
